title: Autorun Organizer 2.13
description:
Autorun Organizer 2.13 

 

Size: 2.3 MB 

Requires: Win 10 / Win 8.1 / Win 7 

 

Autorun Organizer manages startup items and autorun in order to speed boot up times and Windows performance. 

Autorun Organizer Features: 

Speeds up boot up and overall Windows performance 
Manages autorun priorities 
Turns on/off programs in autorun 
Automatically controls disabled programs 

* Just Run to use... 

* Enjoy!
